Page dir
============

Organization
-----------

Generally, individual pages will be placed in their own subdirectories. Nested 
routes with their pages will be subdirectories within the parent page's directory.
Generally, the core of the page will be in `mod.rs`, and page unique components
(not intended to be reusable) will be located in the same dir.


Methodology
-----------

As of 2026/04/15,
The project is primarily meant to be self-hosted, the interactability of SPAs may
be too complex for this project. As such, the fast majority of data should be passed
before page render, i.e. SSR-ed. Islands would be ideal in certain components, such
as a highly interactable table component.
